<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>ESS Portal - Meet the Developers</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    @keyframes fadeIn {
      0% {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(20px);
      }
      100% {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }
    .animate-fadeIn {
      animation: fadeIn 1s ease-in-out;
      opacity: 1 !important;
    }

    @keyframes marquee {
      0%   { transform: translateX(100%); }
      100% { transform: translateX(-100%); }
    }
    .animate-marquee {
      display: inline-block;
      animation: marquee 15s linear infinite;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body class="text-gray-800">
  <%- include('../components/topBanner') %>
  <%- include('../components/navbar') %>

  <!-- Banner -->
  <section class="relative w-full">
    <img src="https://th.bing.com/th/id/OIP.274uZEOGen7RsjVV513XmwHaDt?w=298&h=174&c=7&r=0&o=7&pid=1.7&rm=3" alt="Developers Banner" class="w-full h-96 object-cover">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full bg-black/40 flex items-center justify-center">
      <h1 class="text-white text-4xl font-bold">Meet the Developers</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Developer Section -->
  <section class="text-black py-20 px-6">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">The Team Behind ESS</h2>
      <p class="text-md text-gray-600">
        The Ekhaya Smart Scholars platform was developed by Esgela — a passionate tech education team committed to using technology to unlock opportunity and drive impact in communities.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Mission Cards -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mb-20 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center">
        <i class="fas fa-lightbulb text-3xl text-yellow-400 mb-4"></i>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Innovation-Focused</h3>
        <p class=" text-sm text-gray-600">
          Esgela brings together creativity and technical skill to build digital platforms like ESS that are modern, scalable, and user-centered.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <i class="fas fa-users text-3xl text-yellow-400 mb-4"></i>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Community Driven</h3>
        <p class=" text-sm text-gray-600">
          With deep roots in local communities, the team is dedicated to creating tech that truly serves the needs of learners, educators, and parents.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <i class="fas fa-graduation-cap text-3xl text-yellow-400 mb-4"></i>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Education-Focused</h3>
        <p class=" text-sm text-gray-600">
          As educators themselves, Esgela understands how to integrate technology meaningfully into the learning journey.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <i class="fas fa-code text-3xl text-yellow-400 mb-4"></i>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Built with Purpose</h3>
        <p class=" text-sm text-gray-600">
          Every line of code in the ESS Portal was written with intention — to support learning outcomes and create a seamless user experience.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Founder Card -->
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-md rounded-xl p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center md:items-start gap-8">
      <img src="/images/onwabe.jpg" alt="Onwabe Zibeke" class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full object-cover border-4 border-yellow-400">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Onwabe Zibeke</h3>
        <p class="mb-2">Founder of Esgela</p>
        <p class="mb-4 text-sm text-gray-600">
          Onwabe Zibeke is a software developer and educator who leads the Esgela team. With a passion for community development and digital innovation, Onwabe and his team built the Ekhaya Smart Scholars website to empower learners through accessible, tech-enabled education.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</body>
</html>
